section.section:
"Crime" means an act committed by a person in the State that is a crime under:
common law;
§ 109 of the Code of Public Local Laws of Caroline County;
§ 4-103 of the Code of Public Local Laws of Carroll County;
§ 8A-1 of the Code of Public Local Laws of Talbot County; or
except as provided in paragraph (2) of this subsection, the Annotated Code.
